--></div><header class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 transition-all duration-400 bg-transparent\" style=\"transform:translateY(-80px)\"><nav class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"flex h-16 items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 font-serif text-xl font-normal tracking-tight transition-colors duration-300 text-white\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#52B788] text-[#0F1A14] text-sm font-bold\">IG</span><span class=\"hidden sm:block\">Impact Growth Labs</span></a><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-8\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium transition-colors duration-300 text-white/75 hover:text-white\" href=\"/portfolio\">Projects</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium transition-colors duration-300 text-white/75 hover:text-white\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium transition-colors duration-300 text-white/75 hover:text-white\" href=\"/case-studies\">Case Studies</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium transition-colors duration-300 text-white/75 hover:text-white\" href=\"/what-is-impact\">Whats Impact</a><a class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-300 border border-white/30 bg-white/10 text-white backdrop-blur-sm hover:bg-white/20\" href=\"/portal\">Investor Portal</a></div><button class=\"md:hidden p-2 transition-colors duration-300 text-white\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></nav></header><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)\"><main><main class=\"VenturesPage-module__mmE_CG__page\"><section class=\"Hero-module__vidHHG__hero Hero-module__vidHHG__light\"><div class=\"Hero-module__vidHHG__inner\"><div class=\"FadeIn-module__BD7apG__fadeIn \"><span class=\"EyebrowLabel-module__gRM9Oq__eyebrowLabel \">Ventures</span><h1 class=\"Hero-module__vidHHG__headline\"><span>Founders building for<br/></span><span>all living things.</span></h1><p class=\"Hero-module__vidHHG__subheadline\">We back teams who treat impact not as a marketing claim, but as the natural consequence of how they build, govern, and grow.</p><div class=\"SectionDivider-module__2EY5mW__divider SectionDivider-module__2EY5mW__medium Hero-module__vidHHG__divider\"></div><p class=\"Hero-module__vidHHG__secondaryLine\">Named after the university that lasted 700 years. Investing with a thousand-year horizon.</p><div class=\"Hero-module__vidHHG__ctas\"><a class=\"Button-module__DRR6_W__btn Button-module__DRR6_W__contained \" href=\"/connect?type=founder\">Tell us about your work →</a><a class=\"Button-module__DRR6_W__btn Button-module__DRR6_W__text \" href=\"/philosophy\">Explore our philosophy →</a></div></div></div><div class=\"Hero-module__vidHHG__scrollIndicator\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"Hero-module__vidHHG__scrollText\">Scroll</span><div class=\"Hero-module__vidHHG__scrollLine\"></div></div></section><section class=\"VenturesPage-module__mmE_CG__section VenturesPage-module__mmE_CG__sectionLight\"><div class=\"VenturesPage-module__mmE_CG__inner\"><div class=\"VenturesPage-module__mmE_CG__headerText\"><p class=\"VenturesPage-module__mmE_CG__sectionLabel\">Where we focus</p><h2 class=\"VenturesPage-module__mmE_CG__sectionTitle\">Three doors into the same story.</h2><p class=\"VenturesPage-module__mmE_CG__sectionBody\">We do not chase every theme that trends. We return, again and again, to a small set of questions: How does this venture change the relationship between people and planet? What remains for the seventh generation? Where is there already quiet, patient work happening that deserves to be amplified?</p></div><div class=\"VenturesPage-module__mmE_CG__gridFocusAreas\"><div class=\"FadeIn-module__BD7apG__fadeIn \"><div class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__card\"><div class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><h3 class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__title\">Living food systems</h3><p class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__body\">Ventures reimagining how we grow, distribute, and share food — in ways that nourish soil, communities, and culture at the same time.</p><div class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__questions\"><p class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__questionsLabel\">We ask:</p><ul class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__questionsList\"><li class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__question\">What happens to this place after a hundred harvests?</li><li class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__question\">Who is better fed — and who might be left out?</li><li class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__question\">How does this restore relationship between people and land?</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"FadeIn-module__BD7apG__fadeIn \"><div class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__card\"><div class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><h3 class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__title\">Regenerative energy &amp; infrastructure</h3><p class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__body\">Founders building power, water, and mobility systems that make life gentler on the planet while expanding access for those most often excluded.</p><div class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__questions\"><p class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__questionsLabel\">We ask:</p><ul class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__questionsList\"><li class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__question\">What is the true cost of each unit of energy over a thousand years?</li><li class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__question\">Whose resilience increases when this infrastructure arrives?</li><li class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__question\">Where does this system return more than it takes?</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"FadeIn-module__BD7apG__fadeIn \"><div class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__card\"><div class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><h3 class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__title\">Learning, health, and inner work</h3><p class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__body\">Companies that tend to the inner and outer conditions for human flourishing — education, mental health, care work, and the spaces between them.</p><div class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__questions\"><p class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__questionsLabel\">We ask:</p><ul class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__questionsList\"><li class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__question\">What kind of human being does this product help shape?</li><li class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__question\">How does this reduce suffering without creating new forms of it?</li><li class=\"FocusAreaCard-module__n-g_IW__question\">What becomes possible in a community that fully receives this?</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"Interlude-module__747IUW__interlude Interlude-module__747IUW__indigo\"><div class=\"FadeIn-module__BD7apG__fadeIn Interlude-module__747IUW__inner\"><blockquote class=\"Interlude-module__747IUW__quote\">Everything is connected.<br/><em class=\"gold\">We invest accordingly.</em></blockquote><p class=\"Interlude-module__747IUW__subtext\">This is not a slogan. It is our underwriting criteria.</p></div></div><section class=\"VenturesPage-module__mmE_CG__section VenturesPage-module__mmE_CG__sectionWhite\"><div class=\"VenturesPage-module__mmE_CG__inner\"><div class=\"VenturesPage-module__mmE_CG__headerText\"><p class=\"VenturesPage-module__mmE_CG__sectionLabel\">The portfolio</p><h2 class=\"VenturesPage-module__mmE_CG__sectionTitle\">A living ledger of relationship.</h2><p class=\"VenturesPage-module__mmE_CG__sectionBody\">The ventures we back are not transactions on a cap table. They are long-standing relationships with people who are willing to build slowly, coherently, and with deep accountability to all living things. The examples below are placeholders — this canvas is ready for the real stories.</p></div><div class=\"VenturesPage-module__mmE_CG__gridVentures\"><div class=\"FadeIn-module__BD7apG__fadeIn \"><div class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__card\"><div class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__header\"><h3 class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__name\">[PLACEHOLDER: portfolio company name]</h3><div class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__tags\"><span class=\"Tag-module__SiXDDq__tag Tag-module__SiXDDq__gold\">[PLACEHOLDER: focus area]</span><span class=\"Tag-module__SiXDDq__tag Tag-module__SiXDDq__sage\">[PLACEHOLDER: stage]</span></div></div><p class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__description\">[PLACEHOLDER: one-line description of the venture]</p><p class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__whatDrewUs\">[PLACEHOLDER: what drew us — 2–3 sentences in Nalanda voice]</p><blockquote class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__quote\">“<!-- -->[TESTIMONIAL PLACEHOLDER: founder quote]<!-- -->”</blockquote></div></div><div class=\"FadeIn-module__BD7apG__fadeIn \"><div class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__card\"><div class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__header\"><h3 class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__name\">[PLACEHOLDER: portfolio company name]</h3><div class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__tags\"><span class=\"Tag-module__SiXDDq__tag Tag-module__SiXDDq__gold\">[PLACEHOLDER: focus area]</span><span class=\"Tag-module__SiXDDq__tag Tag-module__SiXDDq__sage\">[PLACEHOLDER: stage]</span></div></div><p class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__description\">[PLACEHOLDER: one-line description of the venture]</p><p class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__whatDrewUs\">[PLACEHOLDER: what drew us — 2–3 sentences in Nalanda voice]</p><blockquote class=\"VentureCard-module__bIq9Eq__quote\">“<!-- -->[TESTIMONIAL PLACEHOLDER: founder quote]<!-- -->”</blockquote></div></div><div class=\"FadeIn-module__BD7apG__fadeIn \"><div class=\"VentureCard-module__b